window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Cara Stone is a broken woman: penniless, homeless, and hopeless. When given the chance to appear on television, she jumps at the opportunity to win a minimum of $5,000 for her family. </p> <p>The state-run, crowdfunded series, <i>Revolver</i>, has been established by the nation's moneyed elite to combat the increasing plight of class warfare. </p> <p>There's never been a <i>Revolver</i> contestant quite like Cara before. The corporate states of America are hungry for blood, and she promises to deliver. </p>"; 
